<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Expression on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/expression/</link><description>Recent content in Expression on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/expression/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Bash Syntax Error in Expression (Arithmetic Error)</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/bash/arithmetic-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/bash/arithmetic-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="bash-syntax-error-in-expression-arithmetic-error-fix"&gt;Bash Syntax Error in Expression (Arithmetic Error) Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when Bash encounters an invalid arithmetic expression inside &lt;code&gt;$(( ))&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;let&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;(( ))&lt;/code&gt;, or &lt;code&gt;expr&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bash evaluates arithmetic expressions using integer math. When the expression contains syntax errors — such as unmatched parentheses, invalid operators, or non-numeric values — the evaluation fails.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Unmatched parentheses&lt;/strong&gt; — &lt;code&gt;$(( 3 + (2 * 1))&lt;/code&gt; missing a closing paren.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Division by zero&lt;/strong&gt; — &lt;code&gt;$(( 10 / 0 ))&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Non-numeric values&lt;/strong&gt; — &lt;code&gt;let result=$var + 1&lt;/code&gt; where &lt;code&gt;$var&lt;/code&gt; contains text.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Using Bash 3 syntax in newer versions&lt;/strong&gt; — or vice versa, with incompatible constructs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-balance-all-parentheses"&gt;Fix 1: Balance all parentheses&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;echo &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;$((&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;))&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Right&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;echo &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;$((&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;))&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Or more complex&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;echo &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;$((&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;))&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-guard-against-division-by-zero"&gt;Fix 2: Guard against division by zero&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;divisor&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[[&lt;/span&gt; $divisor -ne &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]]&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; result&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;$((&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; divisor &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;))&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; echo &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Cannot divide by zero&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;fi&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-validate-variables-are-numeric-before-arithmetic"&gt;Fix 3: Validate variables are numeric before arithmetic&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[[&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$var&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;~ ^&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;0-9&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;+$ &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]]&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; result&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;$((&lt;/span&gt; var &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;))&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; echo &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Not a number: &lt;/span&gt;$var&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;fi&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-use-expr-for-safe-arithmetic-with-error-handling"&gt;Fix 4: Use &lt;code&gt;expr&lt;/code&gt; for safe arithmetic with error handling&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;expr &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt; + &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; 2&amp;gt;&amp;amp;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;||&lt;/span&gt; echo &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Arithmetic failed&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ echo &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;$((&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;))&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;bash: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt; + : syntax error in expression
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ echo &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;$((&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;))&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;bash: division by &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ let result&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;abc&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; + &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;bash: let: result&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;abc&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; + 1: syntax error in expression
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="bad-substitution"&gt;Bad Substitution&lt;/a&gt; — incorrect variable expansion in arithmetic contexts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="conditional-expr"&gt;Conditional Expression Expected&lt;/a&gt; — errors in test expressions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Python SyntaxError — Starred Assignment Target Must Be In List or Tuple</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/python/star-expression/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/python/star-expression/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="syntaxerror--starred-assignment-target-must-be-in-list-or-tuple"&gt;SyntaxError — Starred Assignment Target Must Be In List or Tuple&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;SyntaxError&lt;/code&gt; with the message &amp;ldquo;starred assignment target must be in a list or tuple&amp;rdquo; is raised when you use a starred expression (&lt;code&gt;*variable&lt;/code&gt;) as a standalone assignment target instead of inside a list or tuple. Star expressions can only appear in unpacking contexts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Star expressions (&lt;code&gt;*variable&lt;/code&gt;) are used for extended iterable unpacking. They capture &amp;ldquo;remaining&amp;rdquo; elements from a sequence. However, they must appear inside a list &lt;code&gt;[...]&lt;/code&gt;, tuple &lt;code&gt;(...)&lt;/code&gt;, or as part of a function call. Using &lt;code&gt;*variable&lt;/code&gt; as a direct assignment target is not allowed.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Python SyntaxError — Walrus Operator Invalid Syntax</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/python/walrus-operator/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/python/walrus-operator/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="syntaxerror--walrus-operator-invalid-syntax"&gt;SyntaxError — Walrus Operator Invalid Syntax&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;SyntaxError&lt;/code&gt; with the message &amp;ldquo;invalid syntax&amp;rdquo; when using the walrus operator &lt;code&gt;:=&lt;/code&gt; is raised when you use this operator in a context where it&amp;rsquo;s not allowed, or when using it in Python versions before 3.8. The walrus operator was introduced in Python 3.8 (PEP 572).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The walrus operator &lt;code&gt;:=&lt;/code&gt; allows assignment expressions inside other expressions. It assigns a value to a variable as part of a larger expression. However, it has restrictions: it cannot be used at the top level, in function arguments (in some contexts), or in certain other positions.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] R Error — Error in Eval Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/r/error-in-eval/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/r/error-in-eval/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="error-in-eval--fix"&gt;Error in Eval — Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The error &lt;code&gt;Error in eval(expr, envir, enclos) : ...&lt;/code&gt; occurs when R fails to evaluate an expression. This is often a wrapper error that hides the real cause, such as undefined variables or invalid operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Cause 1: Undefined variable in expression&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;eval&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;parse&lt;/span&gt;(text &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;x + 1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Error in eval: object &amp;#39;x&amp;#39; not found&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Cause 2: Invalid expression&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;eval&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;parse&lt;/span&gt;(text &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;1 + + 2&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Error in eval: unexpected &amp;#39;+&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Cause 3: Error in data frame operations&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;df &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data.frame&lt;/span&gt;(x &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;eval&lt;/span&gt;(df&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;x &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; non_existent) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Error in eval&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Cause 4: Expression referencing missing objects&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;expr &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;quote&lt;/span&gt;(y &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;eval&lt;/span&gt;(expr) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Error in eval: object &amp;#39;y&amp;#39; not found&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-define-variables-before-eval"&gt;Fix 1: Define variables before eval&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;eval&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;parse&lt;/span&gt;(text &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;x + 1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;x &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;eval&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;parse&lt;/span&gt;(text &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;x + 1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Works: returns 11&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-use-trycatch-for-safe-evaluation"&gt;Fix 2: Use tryCatch for safe evaluation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;eval&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;parse&lt;/span&gt;(text &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; user_input))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;tryCatch&lt;/span&gt;(
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;eval&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;parse&lt;/span&gt;(text &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; user_input)),
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; error &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;(e) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;cat&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Evaluation error:&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;conditionMessage&lt;/span&gt;(e), &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;\n&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;NULL&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-check-environment-before-eval"&gt;Fix 3: Check environment before eval&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;eval&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;quote&lt;/span&gt;(x &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; y)) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# y not defined&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;x &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;y &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;eval&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;quote&lt;/span&gt;(x &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; y)) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Works: returns 8&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-use-local-environment-for-isolation"&gt;Fix 4: Use local environment for isolation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Wrong — pollutes global environment&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;eval&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;parse&lt;/span&gt;(text &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;result &amp;lt;- complex_calculation()&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Correct — use local environment&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;env &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;new.env&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;env&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;x &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;env&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;y &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;20&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;eval&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;quote&lt;/span&gt;(x &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; y), envir &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; env) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# result: 30&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 1: Missing variable in eval&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;eval&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;parse&lt;/span&gt;(text &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;my_var + 1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Error in eval(parse(text = &amp;#34;my_var + 1&amp;#34;)) : object &amp;#39;my_var&amp;#39; not found&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 2: Invalid expression&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;eval&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;parse&lt;/span&gt;(text &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;if TRUE print(&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;)&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Error in eval(parse(text = &amp;#34;if TRUE print(&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;)&amp;#34;)) : unexpected symbol&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 3: eval with data&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;df &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;data.frame&lt;/span&gt;(a &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;, b &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;eval&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;quote&lt;/span&gt;(a &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; b), envir &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; df)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Returns: 7, 9, 11, 13, 15&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 4: Nested eval&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;x &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;eval&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;eval&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;quote&lt;/span&gt;(x &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;))) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Works: returns 10&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/r/object-not-found/"&gt;object-not-found&lt;/a&gt; — undefined variable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/r/error-in-parse/"&gt;error-in-parse&lt;/a&gt; — syntax errors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/r/error-in-source/"&gt;error-in-source&lt;/a&gt; — sourcing files&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] TypeScript TS1109 — Expression Expected</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts1109/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts1109/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="ts1109--expression-expected"&gt;TS1109 — Expression expected&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TS1109 is a parse error indicating TypeScript encountered a token where it expected an expression. This usually happens with malformed function calls, missing operands, or incomplete code.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Empty function call argument
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;result&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Math.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;random&lt;/span&gt;() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Missing closing paren or argument
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Missing right operand
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; ; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS1109: expression expected after &amp;#39;+&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Incomplete arrow function
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fn&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; () &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS1109: expression expected after &amp;#39;=&amp;gt;&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 4: Missing value in assignment
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;obj&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;key&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS1109: expression expected after &amp;#39;:&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="solutions"&gt;Solutions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-complete-the-expression"&gt;Fix 1: Complete the expression&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; ;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-close-parentheses-and-provide-arguments"&gt;Fix 2: Close parentheses and provide arguments&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;result&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Math.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;random&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;result&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Math.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;random&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-provide-a-return-value-for-arrow-functions"&gt;Fix 3: Provide a return value for arrow functions&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fn&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; () &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fn&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; () &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;42&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Or with block body
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fn&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; () &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;42&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-complete-object-property-values"&gt;Fix 4: Complete object property values&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;obj&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;key&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;obj&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;key&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;value&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Incomplete template literal
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;`Hello, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS1109
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fix:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;`Hello, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;user&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: Missing argument in new expression
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;el&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;HTMLElement&lt;/span&gt;(); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// If HTMLElement isn&amp;#39;t defined
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS1109 if the expression can&amp;#39;t be resolved
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
